</section>

<!-- ===== ABOUT ===== -->
<section class="section about-section" id="about">
  <div class="section-head">
    <span class="section-num">02</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>
        I'm a self-taught infrastructure engineer who loves building systems that just <em>work</em>. From proxy setups that bypass network restrictions to bot frameworks that automate the boring stuff.
      </p>
      <p>
        My philosophy: <strong>practical over theoretical</strong>. I don't chase shiny frameworks — I pick the right tool for the job and make it rock-solid.
      </p>
      <p>
        Currently focused on <strong>automation</strong>, <strong>anti-detection systems</strong>, and <strong>Web3 integrations</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-cards">
      <div class="about-card">
        <h4>🎯 Focus</h4>
        <p>Infrastructure, security, and scalable backend systems</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <h4>🛠 Approach</h4>
        <p>Build → Test → Ship → Iterate. Fast cycles, real-world results.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <h4>🌍 Location</h4>
        <p>Indonesia — open to remote work worldwide</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <h4>📫 Reach</h4>
        <p>Telegram fastest. Email for formal inquiries.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

